rows.label: tev057801_MSG0001
rows.name:
Simius are seen in pairs, right? Well, once upon time,
those simius were Nopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0002
rows.name:
Two Nopon lovers not get permission to marry
because one family think they better than other family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0003
rows.name:
And so lovers promise to be reborn as simius because
all simius are equal. Then lovers throw selves off
Everwhelm Falls to end it all! Kerplunge![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0004
rows.name:
...What does friend think? Does friend like sad and
moving tale that springs from brain of Gotsu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0008
rows.name: Gotsu never got to know real dadapon very well...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0009
rows.name:
Brotherpon Tatsu is the one Gotsu really ought to
call dadapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0010
rows.name:
Gotsu want to tell dadapon all the fairy tales that
Gotsu make up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0011
rows.name:
Then dadapon can sell them as book,
rake in huge coin, and live on easy street![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0012
rows.name:
THEN rich dadapon not have to worry about getting
smacked around by human friends and... Oh, meh!
Gotsu starting to lose track of plot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0021
rows.name:
Lot of creatures in Noctilum look like flowers and trees,
but does friend know why?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0022
rows.name:
Because they are all playing hide-and-seek!
Critters are cursed to play hide-and-seek forever until
someone find them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0023
rows.name:
Can friend hear their doomed voices echoing through
forest now? "Find critter... Set critter free..."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0024
rows.name:
...What does friend think? Does friend like the eerie,
chilling tale of Gotsu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Gotsu about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0016
rows.name:
Gotsu headed right to Sunlit Spring after Satsu went
missing. Does friend know why?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0017
rows.name:
Because Gotsu heard about strange box that is
supposed to be there! Not because of worry for Satsu.
...Apologies to brotherpon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0018
rows.name:
Anyway, Gotsu get there and found strange box,
but it was burnt to crisp and broken![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0019
rows.name:
What happened to big box? Who is strong and mean
and growly enough to do that kind of damage?
Gotsu smell something fishy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057801_MSG0020
rows.name:
Meh heh. Now Gotsu just have to come up with
epic tale so someone can turn it into bestselling book
and make Gotsu crazy rich![ST:wait ]
